{"tid":2371031,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"律政司重金外聘英大狀任主控惹爭議　港學者促聘用本地大律師","createTime":"2021-01-18T13:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T23:27:03.000Z","uid":230530,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"be323c6e12cd20dc7f7f958c46602f7ab5f994e5","tid":2371031,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:01:27.000Z","msg":"David Perry受聘處理的案件，是民陣於2019年8月18日發起港島區集會及遊行，由黎智英牽頭帶領示威者開始流水式集會，而前議員梁耀忠和區諾軒、民主黨李柱銘、楊森、何俊仁及單仲偕、工黨李卓人及何秀蘭、公民黨吳靄儀、社民連梁國雄亦多次在遊行中牽頭，手持橫額及帶領示威者，他們分別被控涉嫌組織及參與未經批准的集結等罪名，案件將於2月16日在區域法院開審。<br />\n<br />\n對於港府在今次涉及多名泛民的案件，外聘委任David Perry的做法，香港理工大學專業及持續教育學院講師陳偉強表示，理解David Perry的往績對案件勝算有保證，惟現時英方向其施壓，擔心影響審訊，促請港府嚴正考慮停止聘用David Perry。<br />\n<br />\n陳又斥，相信香港亦有能勝任主控官的大律師，不明白律政司為何不聘用本地大狀。他狠批，事件反映律政司中崇洋媚外的陋習猶存，而外聘外籍大狀作主控官亦是極富殖民地色彩的作風，炮轟鄭若驊責無旁貸，敦促鄭應帶頭改變，日後在涉及敏感政治人物的案件中，不要再外聘外籍大狀，以淡化殖民地氣息。"},{"pid":"bb6e6bb691572badd769f3d9759e0c11a5ea5212","tid":2371031,"uid":50386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"乜都關陳偉強事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66bf6a9578dd27d9f7df1eb1bd47296bff17cd38","tid":2371031,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"支持陳生"},{"pid":"65c87da5c4c606ebba05423e3ecfed023aa013e3","tid":2371031,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb6e6bb691572badd769f3d9759e0c11a5ea5212","tid":2371031,"uid":50386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"乜都關陳偉強事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"今次同意喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ca306a1b4ee94cded0fb947451a6e433bed214","tid":2371031,"uid":76133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:06:31.000Z","msg":"用大陸檢察官"},{"pid":"e55094ba4fb7f67ef9082fe946cc9b07fe4b7382","tid":2371031,"uid":357065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:07:49.000Z","msg":"居然用外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c56ad76d7b13ac64469f4215e7fb69ffba3c29","tid":2371031,"uid":96465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:08:35.000Z","msg":"以紅打紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77dc63c7b533797f64645ab07933569ed7c33f8b","tid":2371031,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5b09157ffcd259f6a76368ad83a8e5295beb61","tid":2371031,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:09:52.000Z","msg":"到時重判可以賴個鬼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4eaeb25eec42e60ad8b98f34bdfb4421af59dc","tid":2371031,"uid":388639,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:12:28.000Z","msg":"個撚樣其實係教咩<br />\n乜柒都搭把閪咀埋嚟"},{"pid":"5b3ca5eae579077acd08af1d6834f8ad8664d127","tid":2371031,"uid":358233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:13:21.000Z","msg":"宣誓左擁護基本法未？"},{"pid":"cd1547fe2e42aac17683e80c412eeef767eb8292","tid":2371031,"uid":139100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"呢個理大教授係咪種族歧視？<br />\n炒得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d059b38868658473295e1c36877bd1324e535c00","tid":2371031,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd1547fe2e42aac17683e80c412eeef767eb8292","tid":2371031,"uid":139100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"呢個理大教授係咪種族歧視？<br />\n炒得<img src=\"/assets/faces/p